Our 5th-7th grade scholars are traveling to Camp Tanuga in May. Please share and sponsor a scholar to attend this amazing experience. For just $100, our scholars get a 3-day camping experience where they participate in archery, rock climbing, and other outdoor activities in Kalkaska, Michigan.
